    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p><code>DownloadManager</code> cannot download to <a href=\"https://commonsware.com/blog/2019/10/06/storage-situation-internal-storage.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">internal storage</a>, as it has no access to that location.</p>\n<p><code>DownloadManager</code> is very limited in modern versions of Android, due to scoped storage restrictions. I recommend that you use something else, such as OkHttp, to download the content within your app to a file that you control, including onto internal storage.</p>\n"
