    "body" : "<p>I ran into the same issue, and sadly there’s no good way around it using <code>DownloadManager</code> due to the scoped storage restrictions!<br />\nI ended up writing a custom downloader with a foreground service to keep it alive across app kills, plus parallel chunked downloads so it performs a bit better than ADM for large files.<br />\nI pulled that code out into an open-source SDK if you want to take a look: <a href=\"https://github.com/void-memories/SteadyFetch\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://github.com/void-memories/SteadyFetch</a></p>\n"
  } ],
